{"tid":2517166,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"同大家介紹下FTX exchange!!","createTime":"2021-05-05T07:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T19:41:46.000Z","uid":131403,"like":1,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a6be3d88ff0e41fe623b57e07180c9c5043ca574","tid":2517166,"uid":131403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T07:05:07.000Z","msg":"FTX exchange<br />\n<br />\nFTX係2019年5月1日成立，當時仲係加密貨幣既熊市，對一間岩岩起步既交易所黎講可謂開左個最差既頭；係咁既條件之下，FTＸ係點樣係短短幾年間發展成日交易量破300億美金既交易所呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNkzjxuNsZsBekMzhu7Heohqnf1HSJS9roZGpSmEibpC1?filename=UeaPAF0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUeaPAF0.png&h=0a23c856&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁就要介紹下FTX既核心人物<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdmfPQRUpr9MocUMqPfCq2Fkug9Hhf9RiYtUWDthxieLx?filename=fqdaj7M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffqdaj7M.png&h=bf5d2d49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSam Bankman-Fried(SBF)<br />\n<br />\nSam Bankman-Fried 就讀於麻省理工物理系，畢業後他先到了華爾街的 Jane Street 擔任國際 ETF 交易員，而這份經歷讓 Sam 熟知各類金融商品及交易系統， 他觀察到了當時的加密貨幣金融機制的缺漏(包含沒有提供槓桿、流通性問題、報價準確度問題)，2017 年 9 月，Sam 毅然決然地辭去了 Jane Street 職業交易員的工作，全心投入加密貨幣金融體系，並創辦了全球頂尖加密貨幣造市商 Alameda Research。<br />\n如今 Alameda Research 已經成為加密貨幣市場中的頂尖造市商，替許多加密貨幣交易所提供了準確的報價服務、套利、量化交易等服務。然而 Sam 並不滿足於只做為加密貨幣交易所的技術背後支持者，2019 年 5 月 1 日，他創立了具有金融創新精神的加密貨幣衍生品交易所 FTX ，再度將新的視野帶入加密貨幣金融市場中<br />\n想了解更多可以上佢個Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SBF_Alameda\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSBF_Alameda&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnzw60zqfRdeCYg0zJNkavsY%3D&h=9e18681d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SBF_Alameda</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再講一下FTX<br />\n<br />\nFTX手續費唔錯，現貨期貨Maker0.02%，Taker0.07%，如果交易量愈大仲會愈黎愈平，如果買埋佢自己既平台幣FTT再鎖倉仲會有額外優惠，如下:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSDJkKFDBjxmrUQxh6wqmDg2R7qC8Rxwq5Xm6cY5NoMHu?filename=Dp6nVGd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDp6nVGd.png&h=692ca0f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n股權代幣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVvTicewvMG6BA3irikcQR9tJTnJg7jBk8Fst6xYSBVkT?filename=kFOmrN4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkFOmrN4.png&h=ca72657d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以想像成24小時唔收市既市場，可以更加靈活佈署自己既資金<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLending:（每個小時結算一次)<br />\n簡單Ｄ黎講其實就係借個資金比FTX，FTX再借比人開孖展，然後FTX再同你分成咁樣，牛市既時候息口係認真唔錯，多既時候見過年化100%以上；少既都見過得5%以下<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔係話搵好多，但好處就真係無乜風險，你唔想借比FTX既時候，禁返個取消等1個鐘就可以拎返你借出去既錢，相當方便，適合唔想冒險又想增值既人<br />\n<br />\n實際操作圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbRfmzm1qVv8f2XRuMc3yBvBW9QmJCUvVyLTHUYJnM2hm?filename=SD8EXUS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSD8EXUS.png&h=f2e86a4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFTT token（FTT）:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFTT係支撐FTX生態既應用代幣，目前FTT已上線FTX，幣安，火幣，BitMax，Bitfinex，CoinEx等多家交易所。<br />\n<br />\n買佢既好處除左上面講既質押令到自己交易手續費更低甚至負之外，仲有可以獲得更多既邀請佣金、平台投票治理同埋空頭額外獎勵等等<br />\n<br />\n就算唔質押，只係持幣都會有額外手續費返還<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcSqSs36Go2Bco8ohDrpnvgvJGwhSVbVT2MJwEsHxxnJ7?filename=hd8EXXG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhd8EXXG.png&h=acc68660&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外FTT仲可以充當你合約既持倉保證金<br />\n<br />\nFTX仲會定時回購返FTT去進行銷毀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbYNHmHs4oHobcM6WVm3oBsu9DQ1jt4KoLNWPSAnufpvS?filename=h67FHpf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh67FHpf.png&h=053d3eb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上年既今日FTT大概仲係3usd一粒既價位到以家高位見過60，對我自己黎講可以話係未來既bnb一樣，當然啦呢個只係我個人睇法。<br />\nFTT既幣價對我黎講其實亦都反映緊FTX近來既飛快既發展速度<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaKV7bbLiSwXmvqSBVHgVbm6w6bcrTUyzFV1zXZPbxjrh?filename=GV8p81W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGV8p81W.png&h=54b2f7d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最重要既係!!!FTX好少會HAND機，至少我自己仲未試過！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇左咁耐，如果真係覺得好既話可以用下面既連結申請(5%手續費折扣)：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ftx.com/#a=FTXCAAA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fftx.com%2F%23a%3DFTXCAAA&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnzw60zqfRdeCYg0zJNkavsY%3D&h=26bc7fdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ftx.com/#a=FTXCAAA</a><br />\n<br />\n想一齊討論幣既亦都可以加入以下嘅TG:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Coindis\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FCoindis&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnzw60zqfRdeCYg0zJNkavsY%3D&h=62046c05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Coindis</a>"},{"pid":"ca2e81dc6245337826b39d6cb1d3dd8203b55349","tid":2517166,"uid":73741,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:38:15.000Z","msg":"Scam"},{"pid":"592e6878597667531eb67c1576bcdf96550b2227","tid":2517166,"uid":77968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:02:16.000Z","msg":"創辦人感覺幾幽默<br />\n缺唔缺女人?"},{"pid":"37ae1bfc87c52c2bc3579545507362d4ba58598d","tid":2517166,"uid":111385,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:35:02.000Z","msg":"咪用樓主referral link <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f1d17a843628de0d6dcc7375acef48d6238b39","tid":2517166,"uid":35623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37ae1bfc87c52c2bc3579545507362d4ba58598d","tid":2517166,"uid":111385,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:35:02.000Z","msg":"咪用樓主referral link <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc282412b64d72bbd4acdb65096b0ebabc5f2e22","tid":2517166,"uid":31572,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ca2e81dc6245337826b39d6cb1d3dd8203b55349","tid":2517166,"uid":